place.name: CADISHEAD
place.gazetteerText: CADISHEAD, a hamlet in Barton-upon-Irwell township, Eccles parish, Lancashire; 4½ miles W of Manchester. It has a post office under Warrington. Pop., 961. (In 1870-72, John Marius Wilson's Imperial Gazetteer of England and Wales)
